'''Moonstone Lake''', located on the outskirts of the [[City/Legends|city]] [[Ussa]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Bellassa/Legends|Bellassa]], was the most distant of the seven [[lake]]s within the city boundaries. Compared to the rest of Ussa, the [[Moonstone District|district]] was grimy: the houses were huddled together and the streets were narrow twined and around one another in a baffling pattern.

